
Overview of noun thought

The noun thought has 4 senses (first 3 from tagged texts)
                                        
1. (70) idea, thought -- (the content of cognition; the main thing you are thinking about; "it was not a good idea"; "the thought never entered my mind")
2. (21) thinking, thought, thought process, cerebration, intellection, mentation -- (the process of using your mind to consider something carefully; "thinking always made him frown"; "she paused for thought")
3. (11) thought -- (the organized beliefs of a period or group or individual; "19th century thought"; "Darwinian thought")
4. opinion, sentiment, persuasion, view, thought -- (a personal belief or judgment that is not founded on proof or certainty; "my opinion differs from yours"; "I am not of your persuasion"; "what are your thoughts on Haiti?")
